abstract: Houston Pilots reports traffic jam of 41 oil tankers along Texas coast; traders say jam is indicative of global supply glut of oil.
lead_paragraph: A traffic jam of oil tankers has emerged along the Texas coast this month, a snarl that some traders see as the latest sign of an unyielding global supply glut.

headline.main: Oil Tanker Traffic Jam Off Texas Is Viewed as Sign of Oversupply
headline.print_headline: Oil Tanker Traffic Jam Off Texas Is Viewed as Sign of Oversupply
